{"tid":410855,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"用吹風機吹模特兒裙底太過份　TGS女Game活動宣佈取消","createTime":"2017-09-23T09:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T03:30:19.000Z","uid":51904,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4512bf81c39f0b0998f99f01099bd4549ab77329","tid":410855,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"有時玩得太過份會適得其反。今次東京電玩展 2017 就有一款以女性學生為題材的射擊遊戲，請來一班模特兒穿上學生制服上台表演。為吸引觀眾，台下工作人員利用吹風機，向著模特兒的裙下猛吹。這活動在社交網路就受到廣大網民評擊，認為太無聊兼低俗。最終相關單位在遊戲展第二日開始停止相關活動，在第三日開始將另有安排。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-09-23-15.46.29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2017-09-23-15.46.29.png&h=5bdff3c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次發生問題的是日本美少女射擊遊戲《ぎゃる☆がん2》(Gal*Gun 2) 的攤位，所屬單位是 Inti Creates。遊戲當中女角將會用槍擊退各種惡魔，而TGS會場中的 MC、模特兒等等上台時突然有人在台下利用吹風機給予大家驚喜。官方的解釋是將印上惡魔的相片夾上模特兒的裙子上，利用風力將這些惡魔吹倒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-09-23-15.47.25-694x464.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2017-09-23-15.47.25-694x464.png&h=f0b225ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/753127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F753127.jpg&h=19e68679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在網民發佈的相片中可看到台上的 MC 拚命抓著自己的裙子。之後還有活動是女模特兒為觀眾提供摑掌或者用腳板踩頭的「獎勵」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/753121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F753121.jpg&h=df898ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過這項活動在網上卻受到批評，認為太無聊、低俗。而遊戲公司亦發現了問題，在公式 Twitter 上宣佈之後的活動中止，而第三日一般公眾開放日之後的活動，將會大幅改動，但各種試玩台的展示就不受影響。看來一些活動雖然看似有趣，但如果太過份的話反而會適得其反。"},{"pid":"6322274b44057842f7c39727afc2b6561ae842c0","tid":410855,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"你吹埋我果份"},{"pid":"3579c09a795047ba397a7cb3e62f5ef4781a506a","tid":410855,"uid":127075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:03:07.000Z","msg":"吹不到的風是臭的"},{"pid":"8d16d36011119e7e670d37ad16af0c896921a402","tid":410855,"uid":79959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:05:35.000Z","msg":"畫面明明應該幾靚<br />\n利申：唔係以看胖次角度睇嘅靚"},{"pid":"48167f2906c53d616b346b47659e6121c61cf0a6","tid":410855,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:23:02.000Z","msg":"GalGun預咗俾人搞"},{"pid":"7086fd051eb1c4698c01ee2c3236da968fa6d44d","tid":410855,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T20:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76739ce50e84285c8cdb13908648152e2285d56d","tid":410855,"uid":45120,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:13:36.000Z","msg":"毒撚真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"be87b32e5a9ed6623662f177d926fd5ef6712b74","tid":410855,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T21:15:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be9c04fe4fa3aa0cb6bbbc8d83248c53e0b839ae","tid":410855,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T22:59:15.000Z","msg":"隔住個moon都聞到臭"},{"pid":"9dafeb0873592779234e1823b1c430c35c65935d","tid":410855,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T23:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9 show<br />\nThey should give due respect to girls,<br />\nalthough all females are MK.</blockquote><br />\n又係你條痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4521a